text: Je south pole traverse (ko lawal je wani do)do mari 1600 km do tokka daga mcmurdo tasha ha do ross mayo yahugo (pole).
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Je south pole traverse (ko lawal je wani do)do mari 1600 km do tokka daga mcmurdo tasha ha do ross mayo yahugo (pole). English: I crossed the Sahara Desert in a car.

text: Hado hedi sera woyla je Machu Picchu don hosere juɗɗum do, ɓurna do ha ɓawo hotoji je baabal kiɗɗum je ha les.
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Hado hedi sera woyla je Machu Picchu don hosere juɗɗum do, ɓurna do ha ɓawo hotoji je baabal kiɗɗum je ha les. English: Hedi hedi sera woyla Machu Picchu don hosere, je Machu Picchu don hosere, je ha les.

text: Enceladus on ɓuri miccita naange, do maccitaa de 90 do temere je naange taffiɗum pat.
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Enceladus on ɓuri miccita naange, do maccitaa de 90 do temere je naange taffiɗum pat. English: Enceladus is a planet in the Kuiper Belt of Kuiper Belt. It is the largest planet in the Kuiper Belt, and the only planet in the Kuiper Belt that is not a planet.

text: Waalaako goddo laarata sai asaama laddum e duuleeji hadow be kooseje do taarii,amma to aa doo der loogo .
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Waalaako goddo laarata sai asaama laddum e duuleeji hadow be kooseje do taarii,amma to aa doo der loogo. English: The Fulfulde language is a Bantu language spoken in the northeastern part of the country.

text: Bana jotta leddi Japan, ɗum leddi danneere on bana leddi Briten.
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Bana jotta leddi Japan, ɗum leddi danneere on bana leddi Briten. English: Bana jotta leddi Japan, leddi danneere on bana leddi Briten.

text: Ha do majum, hendu tarata je Gonu, be indi dum ni bora haako leggal kwakwa ha demgal je Maldives, hendu man yotti doggudu 240 kilometers kala awa fu (149 miles fu awa).
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Ha do majum, hendu tarata je Gonu, be indi dum ni bora haako leggal kwakwa ha demgal je Maldives, hendu man yotti doggudu 240 kilometers kala awa fu (149 miles fu awa). English: Fulfulde, a language spoken in the northeast of Nigeria.

text: Turkeys dumari ndiyam dillata je yari(783,562 Square kilometres)(300,948 sq mi), har (755,688 square kilometres) ha lukkere Asia den bo(23,764 square kilometer) (9,174 sq mi) ha Europe.
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Turkeys dumari ndiyam dillata je yari(783,562 Square kilometres)(300,948 sq mi), har (755,688 square kilometres) ha lukkere Asia den bo(23,764 square kilometer) (9,174 sq mi) ha Europe. English: Turkish Fulfulde is a Turkic language spoken in the northeastern part of the country. It is the official language of the Republic of Turkey.

text: Apiya on wuro chaka je leddi Samowa. Wuro man ɗo dow danŋeere je Upolu bo lutti seɗɗa adadu himɓe je woni totton yotta 40,000.
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Apiya on wuro chaka je leddi Samowa. Wuro man ɗo dow danŋeere je Upolu bo lutti seɗɗa adadu himɓe je woni totton yotta 40,000. English: The Fulfulde language is a Bantu language spoken in the northeastern part of the country.

text: No eyende teddudum man dayi be morsugo leddi, do sada andugo ko wawata wannugo United States ko Caribbean.
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: No eyende teddudum man dayi be morsugo leddi, do sada andugo ko wawata wannugo United States ko Caribbean. English: The Fulfulde language is a Bantu language spoken in the northeastern part of the country.

text: Buri sewugo ha les maria man bo buri tekkugo ha les leddi towinga.
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Buri sewugo ha les maria man bo buri tekkugo ha les leddi towinga. English: Buri sewugo ha les maria man bo buri tekkugo ha les leddi towinga.

text: Ledde je na mangrove swamps ba- ɗo mari kujeji lutti handi mara kujeji handi ha ladde je artini maari suddi molaande ladde.
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Ledde je na mangrove swamps ba- ɗo mari kujeji lutti handi mara kujeji handi ha ladde je artini maari suddi molaande ladde. English: The Fulfulde language is a Bantu language spoken in the northeastern part of the country.

text: Map je jangata dimbugo leddi je lesde yasi je kaeji ha America holli wala dimbugo leddi ha Iceland asawere je sali do.
translated_text: Nigerian Fulfulde: Map je jangata dimbugo leddi je lesde yasi je kaeji ha America holli wala dimbugo leddi ha Iceland asawere je sali do. English: The Fulfulde language is a Bantu language spoken in the northeastern part of the country.

text: Suitugo ha do hosere woni woyla Makkah, wuddere der hosere man do daayi be luttudum duniyaru.
